OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773828292
OL,3,CWoman recovering from meningitis
OL,4,C'frightened to leave hospital' amid
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FShe began developing symptoms
OL,8,Fincluding a headache, which her family
OL,9,Fput down to Covid, but on Saturday,
OL,10,FKeeleigh suffered a seizure and
OL,11,Fcollapsed.
OL,13,FShe is currently recovering in
OL,14,Fhospital.
OL,16,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian , Keeleigh's
OL,17,Fmother Khali Goodwin said it was
OL,18,Fthanks to her flatmates that she's
OL,19,Fstill alive.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773828292
OL,3,CWoman recovering from meningitis
OL,4,C'frightened to leave hospital' amid
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"I literally owe it to her flatmate
OL,8,Fwho kept an eye on her," she said.
OL,10,F"Keeleigh had a seizure, banged her
OL,11,Fhead as she fell, and her housemate
OL,12,Ffound her, rang the ambulance, and if
OL,13,Fit wasn't for her, my daughter
OL,14,Fwouldn't be here.
OL,16,F"I thought it was Covid, so I told her
OL,17,Fjust to sleep it off. Meningitis
OL,18,Fwasn't even on the Richter scale of
OL,19,Fwhat I ever would have thought.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773828292
OL,3,CWoman recovering from meningitis
OL,4,C'frightened to leave hospital' amid
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"It's the last thing I would have
OL,8,Fthought."
OL,10,FThe majority of young people born
OL,11,Fbefore 2015 are not protected against
OL,12,Fmeningitis B unless they have had the
OL,13,Fjab privately. It was introduced on
OL,14,Fthe NHS for babies in 2015.
OL,16,FKhali believes the vaccine should be
OL,17,Fgiven to all young people.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773828292
OL,3,CWoman recovering from meningitis
OL,4,C'frightened to leave hospital' amid
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"I have a 14-year-old, she obviously
OL,8,Fisn't vaccinated with it - my younger
OL,9,Fones will be, and I did look into
OL,10,Fgetting her vaccinated and myself and
OL,11,FKeeley and it's quite an expensive
OL,12,Fthing.
OL,14,F"Keeleigh is 21, she works full time,
OL,15,Fso for her to be spending out hundreds
OL,16,Fof pounds for a vaccine, it's a lot
OL,17,Ffor a young, and all the other
OL,18,Fstudents.
OL,20,F"It's a lot of money for them to be
OL,21,Fforking out."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773828292
OL,3,CWoman recovering from meningitis
OL,4,C'frightened to leave hospital' amid
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FHundreds of people who visited Club
OL,8,FChemistry on March 5, 6 or 7 were told
OL,9,Fto come forward for preventative
OL,10,Fantibiotic treatment as a
OL,11,F"precautionary measure".
OL,13,FBut Khali said Keeleigh had been in
OL,14,FChemistry with friends on Thursday -
OL,15,Fdays after the dates people were
OL,16,Falleged to have been affected.
OL,18,F"The health authorities have singled
OL,19,Fout if you went to the club on 5th,
OL,20,F6th, 7th of March, but Keeley wasn't
OL,21,Fthere until a week later," she added.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773828292
OL,3,CWoman recovering from meningitis
OL,4,C'frightened to leave hospital' amid
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"Why those dates because my daughter
OL,8,Fwent on the 12th and yet a few days
OL,9,Flater she's in hospital fighting for
OL,10,Fher life."
OL,12,FLouise Jones-Roberts, the owner of
OL,13,FClub Chemistry, said more than 2,000
OL,14,Fpeople would have visited the venue
OL,15,Fover the three dates.
OL,17,FThe UKHSA said it is continuing to
OL,18,Finvestigate the outbreak, with 15
OL,19,Fcases of meningitis notified since
OL,20,FMarch 13, including two deaths.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773828292
OL,3,CWoman recovering from meningitis
OL,4,C'frightened to leave hospital' amid
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FA Year 13 pupil in Faversham called
OL,8,FJuliette and a student at the
OL,9,FUniversity of Kent have died - and
OL,10,Fit's understood some people were put
OL,11,Fin an induced coma.
OL,13,FKeeleigh is still being treated in
OL,14,Fhospital, and her mum says she is
OL,15,Fslowly returning to normal. But the
OL,16,Fincident has left her too frightened
OL,17,Fto leave the hospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773828292
OL,3,CWoman recovering from meningitis
OL,4,C'frightened to leave hospital' amid
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"Obviously because her immune system
OL,8,Fis going to be extremely weak, she
OL,9,Fdoesn't want to be going out,
OL,10,Fcertainly doesn't want to be going to
OL,11,Fpublic places, to crowded places.
OL,13,F"It's really shocked her and it's
OL,14,Ffrightened all of us, it really has."
